methods.title: String.prototype.between
methods.description: Registers an event listener callback to this event.

overloads.title: between(startWith: string, endWith: string, include?: boolean): string
overloads.description: Returns the string that between specified start and end string.

parameters.name: startWith
parameters.description: The characters to be searched for at the start of this string.

parameters.name: endWith
parameters.description: The characters to be searched for at the end of this string.

parameters.name: include
parameters.description: If true, return value will include startWith & endwith, else do not include. Default is false.
